'''''naruka''''' is a [[Khuzdul]] word of unknown meaning, stated at one point to the possible origin of the river-name ''[[Narog]]''. The word ''naruka'' was perhaps originally the Khuzdul name of the [[Petty-dwarves]].<ref>{{PE|17}}, p. 47</ref>
